publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-5785 John Scott on behalf of the Scottish Parliamentary Corporate Body: The Scottish Public Services Ombudsman—That the Parliament nominates Professor Alice Brown to Her Majesty The Queen for reappointment as the Scottish Public Services Ombudsman from 30 September 2007 until 29 September 2011.
